#. <section class="sutta" id="sn15.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Pitusutta"
msgstr "15. Father"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.15:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn15.15:1.2"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro … pe …"
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning. …"

msgctxt "sn15.15:1.3"
msgid "na so, bhikkhave, satto sulabharūpo yo napitābhūtapubbo … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It’s not easy to find a sentient being who in all this long time has not "
"previously been your father. …"

msgctxt "sn15.15:1.4"
msgid "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and "
"freed regarding all conditions.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.15:1.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
